Former Liverpool star, Mark Lawrenson, has predicted Premier League match-day 31 fixtures. Manchester United will host Leicester City on Saturday evening, while Arsenal will face Crystal Palace on Monday night. Chelsea will face Brentford at Stamford Bridge on Saturday, and Liverpool will host Watford on Saturday afternoon. Providing his predictions, Lawrenson was quoted by BBC Sport as saying: Liverpool 3-0 Watford
Brighton 2-0 Norwich
Burnley 0-2 Man City
Chelsea 2-0 Brentford
Leeds United 1-1 Southampton
Wolves 1-1 Aston Villa
Man United 2-0 Leicester City
West Ham 2-1 Everton
Tottenham 2-0 Newcastle
Crystal Palace 1-1 Arsenal